Error","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure with an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UnsafeMutableBufferPointer"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"parameter that points to the contiguous storage for the array."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"If no such storage exists, it is created. If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"body"},{"type":"text","text":" has a return value, that value is also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"used as the return value for the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"withUnsafeMutableBufferPointer(_:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method. The pointer argument is valid only for the duration of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"method’s execution."}]}],"name":"body"}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"return-value","text":"Return Value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The return value, if any, of the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"body"},{"text":" closure parameter.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Often, the optimizer can eliminate bounds checks within an array","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"algorithm, but when that fails, invoking the same algorithm on the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"buffer pointer passed into your closure lets you trade safety for speed.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The following example shows how modifying the contents of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"UnsafeMutableBufferPointer","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" argument to "},{"code":"body","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" alters the contents of"},{"type":